{"tid":609030,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[vlog]一個人十日九夜去到先plan既日本東京之旅","createTime":"2018-03-28T16:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T05:00:50.000Z","uid":129530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e5205ef8ddb5c4295c1699552b7a4cea32bceb9b","tid":609030,"uid":129530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打大家好~<br />\n<br />\n小弟兩個星期前去左個十日九夜既東京之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一條友去又無乜野做 就膽粗粗試下將呢個旅程拍左一堆片<br />\n<br />\n一日拍一條 拍完全日，夜晚返到旅舍就剪片<br />\n<br />\n不知不覺就整左11條片出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我係突然想拍 所以D器材好鬼簡單 D片全部都係用部iphone6s剪同拍，收音都只係用個earphone黎錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n襯我仲有印象就想post係到同大家分享下同埋可以俾d意見我<br />\n<br />\n一齊吹下水 等我下次有機會去旅行又可以玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我去d地方可能好行下 大家唔好笑我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwNlzindi9zCOEKq8rtuxDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCwNlzindi9zCOEKq8rtuxDw&d=BpFGe4KMlBFqvrbWS%2BudidU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4d1beab9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCwNlzindi9zCOEKq8rtuxDw</a>"},{"pid":"6bfc7f1dc0ada8951d3e066086a35372638e6d89","tid":609030,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"too long"},{"pid":"4cd0f2d40e67126000b8a785386714073aa86d9b","tid":609030,"uid":129530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bfc7f1dc0ada8951d3e066086a35372638e6d89","tid":609030,"uid":152753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi